OL,6,F"One day I went from being employed
OL,7,Faged in my early 20s, to overnight
OL,8,Fbecoming an advertised escort, a
OL,9,Fheroin addict waking up sick every day
OL,10,Fand stealing from my family to buy
OL,11,Fheroin from him," she says.
OL,13,F"He would supply me with heroin every
OL,14,Fday at the same place and at the same
OL,15,Ftime. However, if I refused to have
OL,16,Fsex with one of the sex-buyers he had
OL,17,Fset me up with, he would not sell me
OL,18,Fany heroin and would block my phone
OL,19,Fnumber, leaving me sick for days.
