OL,6,F"With MacCormack, I lost the right to
OL,7,Fsay yes or no as a girl and as a
OL,8,Fwoman. Sex with paying customers just
OL,9,Fbecame so normal. I would wake up
OL,10,Fevery day merely existing and not
OL,11,Fliving. I hated MacCormack so much,
OL,12,Fbut he had me needing him because of
OL,13,Fhis heroin.
OL,15,F"I am now free from heroin and feel
OL,16,Fstronger than I have in a long time. I
OL,17,Fwill never let anyone treat me the way
OL,18,FMacCormack did."
